mySubtitles.Sub1.myText	My love, I hope this letter finds you well. In my heart I feel I will know if something happens to you. It is so hard to face the day without you by my side...
mySubtitles.Sub2.myText	\nMy dearest Natasha. I'm writing this sitting on a tractor just like those we have on the Kolkhozes back home. They are not so different from us, these Americans...
mySubtitles.Sub3.myText	\nThey have begun working triple shifts at the factory. I am glad that Inessa is not working nights. Many factories have been bombed and I fear...
mySubtitles.Sub4.myText	\nThough, I am a little worried about Kolya. He is very hard on the men and when I tried to talk to him he just shrugged it off. I will have to make it clear that he is under my command...
mySubtitles.Sub5.myText	\nAnd I think about all the boys over there whose mothers cannot sleep for worry. Those serving with you must be the lucky ones, Volodja, for I know that you care deeply for them...
mySubtitles.Sub6.myText	\nI will be home soon enough. Until then, know that I love you. Your Vladimir.
